    "description": "Experience the ultimate zombie survival game where you fight for your life, build your base, loot valuable resources, and face dynamic weather and time-of-day changes. Craft powerful weapons, battle terrifying boss zombies, and embark on a mission to find the anti-virus and save humanity.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SURVIVAL</h2>Navigate a post-apocalyptic world, where every decision can mean life or death. Scavenge for food, water, and supplies to keep your character alive in the face of constant danger.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072270/extras/cadad13f3718bafc2fa684eeafae43c2.avif?t=1724274972\" width=618 height=314 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BASE BUILDING</h2>Construct and fortify your own base to protect against relentless zombie hordes. Customize and upgrade your shelter to create a safe haven and a loading point after death.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072270/extras/2c5289ff0d850a440023b4e7f4451068.avif?t=1724274972\" width=618 height=314 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DAY AND NIGHT CYCLE</h2>Experience a dynamic day and night cycle that affects gameplay and zombie behavior. Adapt your strategies as visibility decreases and the undead become more aggressive after dark.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072270/extras/a02f3b55fc196e8e2c2f5f4a3f0d4409.avif?t=1724274972\" width=618 height=314 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BOSS ZOMBIES</h2>Face off against boss zombies that present challenges and require a lot of equipment to defeat. Each boss will provide valuable rewards.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072270/extras/b282db2088322690f0e0b570825cf06a.avif?t=1724274972\" width=618 height=314 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CRAFTING</h2>Collect materials and craft an arsenal of powerful weapons, armors and much more to defend yourself against the undead.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072270/extras/316260d1891f65ca0c05a307a13eec40.avif?t=1724274972\" width=618 height=314 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FIND THE ANTI-VIRUS</h2>Embark on a critical mission to find the anti-virus and save humanity from extinction. Time is running out, and your actions will determine the fate of the world.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072270/extras/b2df7560277d85a9e9d5f965bc478c4b.avif?t=1724274972\" width=618 height=314 /></span>",
